oai_dc:dc.dc:title: 2010: A Millington Home affected by the flooding waters in May of 2010.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: 2010 flood; Millington, Tennessee; water; residences;
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Taken in Millington where some houses were flooded. House was abandoned and when returned to the next day, 5 inches of standing water filled the house.
